GCP Organisation: acme-corp.com
├── folders/platform
│   ├── project: platform-shared-services      (Backstage, Artifact Registry, monitoring backends)
│   ├── project: platform-networking            (Shared VPC host project, Cloud DNS)
│   └── project: platform-security             (Cloud Security Command Center, audit log sink)
├── folders/workloads
│   ├── folders/development
│   │   └── project: workloads-development     (dev GKE cluster, dev workloads)
